                  \<and> inj f \<Longrightarrow> thesis) \<Longrightarrow> thesis"
                using assms cx f
                unfolding inj_on_def
                by metis
            qed
            have "(change_int f i) ` (props p) \<subseteq> (domain U)"
            proof
